# Kvm

## Creating shared folder

Kvm options

```
-virtfs local,path=/tmp/valgrind,mount_tag=valgrind,security_model=mapped
```

Inside the machine

```
mount -type 9p -o trans=virtio valgrind /media/disk/
```
